comment: I think they need to make an example of Amber Heard. Blacklisting her from Hollywood is not enough. Right now, we have lying under oath numerous times, trying to get others to lie under oath and plotting what story they should stick to when lying under oath, buying off witnesses which theres a lot of evidence of, presenting false evidence, extortion in the first place because none of this would have happened had she gotten everything she wanted from Johnny according to Heard herself, getting many others involved in her scheme through coercion, destruction of property (she ruined a bunch of johnnys stuff throwing things at him, throwing temper tantrums, and literally shitting on his bed), her mocking and threatening phone calls trying to scare Johnny from testifying (tampering with a witness), her literally admitting to assaulting Johnny on phone recordings, a long history of her doing the same thing to others and being physically violent with her exs, just in general being a manipulative piece of trash (including having sexual relations with Elon Musk for her benifit and lying about when this took place), Lying about giving her divorce money to charity (which if she signed something saying she would and then didn't abide by a legal requirement she should be arrested for that) literally cutting Johnnys finger off, and outside of just this case shes made threats and been both verbally and physically abusive to her staff, abused illegal drugs many times, lied about many many things (including faking going to a black lives matter protest after posting racist things, not racist just makes her a terrible human being but speaks to her credibility), and trying to bribe scare or screw anyone who stands against her. Right now, even her lawyer (the same lawyer who represented rapist Harvey Weinstein) quit because she apparently could no longer believe Heard was innocent and didn't want to support an abuser (yeah, supporting AMBER goes against her moral code) and she's been fired and replaced from the new Aquaman movie which is a good start but we should not stop here. With all of this evidence Heard should be arrested. She seems to think she's above the law and not only does she think there will be no repercussions but she sees all of this as a game and she took advantage of the fact women who claim to have been abused are usually believed, she undid years and years of work making women able to speak up and making people listen to them and believe them. I don't like saying things are sexist but if this had been the other way around and Johnny did any of this, cutting off her finger, hitting her, plotting to steal her money then lying under oath about it there'd be no question about it he would be arrested. Her gender doesn't change what she's done. She has hurt so many people, and put Johnny through hell. He didn't deserve this. GIVE JOHNNY JUSTICE
